  "body": [
    {
      "content": "我曾与多个团队合作构建基因工作流",
      "from": 0.12,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 1,
      "to": 3.38
    },
    {
      "content": "我发现其中一个最大预测因素是",
      "from": 3.38,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 2,
      "to": 6.93
    },
    {
      "content": "能否真正做好某件事",
      "from": 6.93,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 3,
      "to": 9.43
    },
    {
      "content": "与效率低下形成对比",
      "from": 9.43,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 4,
      "to": 11.87
    },
    {
      "content": "是否能够驱动严格的评估流程",
      "from": 11.87,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 5,
      "to": 17.14
    },
    {
      "content": "因此你推动评估的能力",
      "from": 17.14,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 6,
      "to": 19.76
    },
    {
      "content": "对基因工作流的构建效果影响巨大",
      "from": 19.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 7,
      "to": 26.07
    },
    {
      "content": "在本视频中",
      "from": 26.07,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 8,
      "to": 26.83
    },
    {
      "content": "我们将快速概述如何构建评估",
      "from": 26.83,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 9,
      "to": 29.81
    },
    {
      "content": "这将是课程后续模块深入探讨的主题",
      "from": 29.81,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 10,
      "to": 35.37
    },
    {
      "content": "因此让我们看看构建一个enworkflow后",
      "from": 35.37,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 11,
      "to": 39.25
    },
    {
      "content": "比如这个用于处理客户订单查询的工作流",
      "from": 39.25,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 12,
      "to": 43.03
    },
    {
      "content": "实际上很难预先知道",
      "from": 43.03,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 13,
      "to": 45.95
    },
    {
      "content": "可能出现哪些问题",
      "from": 45.95,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 14,
      "to": 48.37
    },
    {
      "content": "因此不如在构建评估时",
      "from": 48.37,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 15,
      "to": 51.83
    },
    {
      "content": "我建议",
      "from": 51.83,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 16,
      "to": 52.95
    },
    {
      "content": "只需查看输出结果并手动寻找改进空间",
      "from": 52.95,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 17,
      "to": 59.96
    },
    {
      "content": "例如",
      "from": 59.96,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 18,
      "to": 60.82
    },
    {
      "content": "你可能阅读大量输出内容",
      "from": 60.82,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 19,
      "to": 62.4
    },
    {
      "content": "发现它意外提及竞争对手的情况过多",
      "from": 62.4,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 20,
      "to": 67.689
    },
    {
      "content": "许多企业不希望员工提及竞争对手",
      "from": 67.689,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 21,
      "to": 71.88
    },
    {
      "content": "因为这会制造尴尬局面",
      "from": 71.88,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 22,
      "to": 73.68
    },
    {
      "content": "当你阅读这些输出时",
      "from": 73.68,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 23,
      "to": 75.56
    },
    {
      "content": "可能会发现中心提到",
      "from": 75.56,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 24,
      "to": 77.18
    },
    {
      "content": "我很高兴你们的产品远优于竞争对手",
      "from": 77.18,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 25,
      "to": 80.0
    },
    {
      "content": "竞品代码",
      "from": 80.0,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 26,
      "to": 80.76
    },
    {
      "content": "或有时说当然应该退款",
      "from": 80.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 27,
      "to": 83.32
    },
    {
      "content": "不同于竞品代码",
      "from": 83.32,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 28,
      "to": 84.34
    },
    {
      "content": "我们退货流程更便捷",
      "from": 84.34,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 29,
      "to": 85.5
    },
    {
      "content": "你可能会看到这并感叹",
      "from": 85.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 30,
      "to": 87.31
    },
    {
      "content": "我真的不希望它提及竞争对手",
      "from": 87.31,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 31,
      "to": 90.67
    },
    {
      "content": "这就是一个典型问题",
      "from": 90.67,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 32,
      "to": 92.29
    },
    {
      "content": "这类问题很难在构建工作流前预见",
      "from": 92.29,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 33,
      "to": 97.15
    },
    {
      "content": "最佳实践是先构建系统",
      "from": 97.15,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 34,
      "to": 99.35
    },
    {
      "content": "然后检查找出不足之处",
      "from": 99.35,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 35,
      "to": 103.639
    },
    {
      "content": "并找到评估和改进的方法",
      "from": 103.639,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 36,
      "to": 107.499
    },
    {
      "content": "消除仍不满意的环节",
      "from": 107.499,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 37,
      "to": 111.19
    },
    {
      "content": "假设企业认为提及竞争对手是错误",
      "from": 111.19,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 38,
      "to": 118.13
    },
    {
      "content": "那么",
      "from": 118.13,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 39,
      "to": 118.65
    },
    {
      "content": "在消除这些竞争维度时",
      "from": 118.65,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 40,
      "to": 121.97
    },
    {
      "content": "一种跟踪进展的方式是添加评估",
      "from": 121.97,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 41,
      "to": 126.52
    },
    {
      "content": "统计此类错误发生频率",
      "from": 126.52,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 42,
      "to": 128.9
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你有竞争对手名单如竞品公司",
      "from": 128.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 43,
      "to": 132.46
    },
    {
      "content": "竞对代码",
      "from": 132.46,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 44,
      "to": 133.12
    },
    {
      "content": "其他公司",
      "from": 133.12,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 45,
      "to": 134.03
    },
    {
      "content": "则可编写代码在输出中搜索",
      "from": 134.03,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 46,
      "to": 138.14
    },
    {
      "content": "统计提及竞争对手名称的频率",
      "from": 138.14,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 47,
      "to": 141.64
    },
    {
      "content": "并计算为整体响应的比例",
      "from": 141.64,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 48,
      "to": 145.98
    },
    {
      "content": "统计误提竞争对手的频率",
      "from": 145.98,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 49,
      "to": 149.55
    },
    {
      "content": "关于竞争维度的问题有一个客观指标",
      "from": 149.55,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 50,
      "to": 155.39
    },
    {
      "content": "这意味着要么提到了竞争对手，要么没有提到",
      "from": 155.39,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 51,
      "to": 157.91
    },
    {
      "content": "而对于客观标准",
      "from": 157.91,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 52,
      "to": 160.41
    },
    {
      "content": "你可以编写代码检查该特定错误发生的频率",
      "from": 160.41,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 53,
      "to": 166.479
    },
    {
      "content": "但因为Elm的输出",
      "from": 166.479,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 54,
      "to": 168.179
    },
    {
      "content": "自由文本也将成为你评估此输出的标准之一",
      "from": 168.179,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 55,
      "to": 172.86
    },
    {
      "content": "这可能更具主观性",
      "from": 172.86,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 56,
      "to": 174.74
    },
    {
      "content": "而编写代码生成黑白评分会更困难",
      "from": 174.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 57,
      "to": 179.18
    },
    {
      "content": "在这种情况下",
      "from": 179.18,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 58,
      "to": 180.24
    },
    {
      "content": "使用LLM作为裁判是评估输出的常见技术",
      "from": 180.24,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 59,
      "to": 185.74
    },
    {
      "content": "例如",
      "from": 185.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 60,
      "to": 186.42
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你在构建一个研究代理来处理不同主题的研究",
      "from": 186.42,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 61,
      "to": 190.6
    },
    {
      "content": "然后可以使用另一个LLM并提示它",
      "from": 190.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 62,
      "to": 194.32
    },
    {
      "content": "也许说",
      "from": 194.32,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 63,
      "to": 195.1
    },
    {
      "content": "为以下文章分配1到5分的质量评分",
      "from": 195.1,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 64,
      "to": 198.34
    },
    {
      "content": "其中1分是最差，5分是最好的文章",
      "from": 198.34,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 65,
      "to": 202.08
    },
    {
      "content": "我用Python表达式表示",
      "from": 202.08,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 66,
      "to": 205.12
    },
    {
      "content": "你知道的",
      "from": 205.12,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 67,
      "to": 205.52
    },
    {
      "content": "将生成的文章复制粘贴到这里",
      "from": 205.52,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 68,
      "to": 207.62
    },
    {
      "content": "因此可以提示LLM阅读文章并为其分配质量评分",
      "from": 207.62,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 69,
      "to": 212.69
    },
    {
      "content": "然后我让研究代理撰写多份不同研究报告",
      "from": 212.69,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 70,
      "to": 217.0
    },
    {
      "content": "例如关于黑洞科学的最新进展",
      "from": 217.0,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 71,
      "to": 220.48
    },
    {
      "content": "或使用机器人采摘水果",
      "from": 220.48,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 72,
      "to": 222.9
    },
    {
      "content": "然后在这个例子中",
      "from": 222.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 73,
      "to": 224.76
    },
    {
      "content": "裁判LLM可能给黑洞文章打3分",
      "from": 224.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 74,
      "to": 229.54
    },
    {
      "content": "机器人采摘文章得4分",
      "from": 229.54,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 75,
      "to": 232.35
    },
    {
      "content": "当你不断改进研究代理时",
      "from": 232.35,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 76,
      "to": 235.07
    },
    {
      "content": "希望这些分数会随时间逐渐提升",
      "from": 235.07,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 77,
      "to": 237.86
    },
    {
      "content": "顺便说一句，Ohm实际上在这方面并不太擅长",
      "from": 237.86,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 78,
      "to": 241.88
    },
    {
      "content": "至少在1到5分的评分尺度上",
      "from": 241.88,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 79,
      "to": 243.96
    },
    {
      "content": "你可以试试看",
      "from": 243.96,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 80,
      "to": 244.78
    },
    {
      "content": "但我个人很少使用这种技术",
      "from": 244.78,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 81,
      "to": 247.98
    },
    {
      "content": "但在后续模块中你会学到更好的方法来评估输出",
      "from": 247.98,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 82,
      "to": 252.76
    },
    {
      "content": "获得比1到5分评分更准确的分数",
      "from": 252.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 83,
      "to": 256.46
    },
    {
      "content": "尽管有些人会这样做",
      "from": 256.46,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 84,
      "to": 258.289
    },
    {
      "content": "或许作为初步筛选",
      "from": 258.289,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 85,
      "to": 259.689
    },
    {
      "content": "作为裁判类型的评估",
      "from": 259.689,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 86,
      "to": 262.249
    },
    {
      "content": "仅作为后续将学习的AI评估方法的预览",
      "from": 262.249,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 87,
      "to": 267.26
    },
    {
      "content": "在这门课程中",
      "from": 267.26,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 88,
      "to": 268.0
    },
    {
      "content": "你已经听过我如何编写代码评估客观标准",
      "from": 268.0,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 89,
      "to": 272.889
    },
    {
      "content": "例如是否提及了竞争对手",
      "from": 272.889,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 90,
      "to": 274.689
    },
    {
      "content": "或使用LLM作为更主观标准的裁判",
      "from": 274.689,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 91,
      "to": 277.709
    },
    {
      "content": "例如这篇文章的质量如何",
      "from": 277.709,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 92,
      "to": 279.46
    },
    {
      "content": "但后续你将学习两种主要评估方法",
      "from": 279.46,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 93,
      "to": 282.3
    },
    {
      "content": "一种是端到端评估",
      "from": 282.3,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 94,
      "to": 283.32
    },
    {
      "content": "测量整个代理的输出质量",
      "from": 283.32,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 95,
      "to": 286.919
    },
    {
      "content": "以及组件级评估",
      "from": 286.919,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 96,
      "to": 288.999
    },
    {
      "content": "我们可能测量工作流程中单一步骤的输出质量",
      "from": 288.999,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 97,
      "to": 293.84
    },
    {
      "content": "这些方法对驱动开发过程不同部分非常有用",
      "from": 293.84,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 98,
      "to": 298.49
    },
    {
      "content": "而我经常做的一件事",
      "from": 298.49,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 99,
      "to": 300.77
    },
    {
      "content": "就是检查中间输出或称为LLM的追踪记录",
      "from": 300.77,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 100,
      "to": 306.03
    },
    {
      "content": "为了理解它未能达到我的预期之处",
      "from": 306.03,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 101,
      "to": 310.03
    },
    {
      "content": "我们称之为错误分析",
      "from": 310.03,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 102,
      "to": 312.07
    },
    {
      "content": "我们只需通读中间输出结果",
      "from": 312.07,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 103,
      "to": 314.43
    },
    {
      "content": "每一步都尝试发现改进机会",
      "from": 314.43,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 104,
      "to": 317.7
    },
    {
      "content": "结果发现能够执行恶行",
      "from": 317.7,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 105,
      "to": 319.54
    },
    {
      "content": "S和错误分析是一项关键技能",
      "from": 319.54,
      "location": 2,
